===Etymology 1===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*ters-}}
From {{inh|en|enm|test}}, {{m|enm|teste}}, from {{der|en|fro|test}}, {{m|fro|teste|t=an earthen vessel, especially a pot in which metals were tried}}, from {{der|en|la|testum|t=the lid of an earthen vessel, an earthen vessel, an earthen pot}}, from {{m|la|*terstus}}, past participle of the root {{m|la|*tersa||dry land}}. See [[terra]], [[thirst]].

